the location parameter where your did document history can be found.

00:12:24.120 --> 00:12:26.880
Your verifiable did document history can be found.

00:12:26.880 --> 00:12:29.820
So the did methods will evolve.

00:12:29.820 --> 00:12:31.930
This is all fine and fine and good.

00:12:31.940 --> 00:12:38.020
What's still open is someone needs to run this box and

00:12:38.020 --> 00:12:44.720
that someone has a couple of things to decide.

00:12:46.320 --> 00:12:50.580
Currently, the public knowledge that was given by the Blue Sky

00:12:50.580 --> 00:12:55.210
Project is the claim that the Swiss Association is being founded or

00:12:55.210 --> 00:12:57.020
has been founded, I've heard.

