If you want to contribute, please leave your comments.

00:22:33.640 --> 00:22:39.320
We should assume that science is always under threat.

00:22:39.360 --> 00:22:40.840
The current U.

00:22:40.850 --> 00:22:41.320
S.

00:22:41.340 --> 00:22:45.160
administration is on camera saying things like, we have to attack

00:22:45.160 --> 00:22:46.040
the universities.

00:22:46.100 --> 00:22:48.920
So, there the mission is clear.

00:22:48.920 --> 00:22:52.690
And a few citations on what I think is now important

00:22:52.690 --> 00:22:57.070
to remember in this situation is that there is no such thing

00:22:57.210 --> 00:22:58.440
as post-truth.

00:22:59.720 --> 00:23:01.230
I hope we can agree on that.

00:23:01.440 --> 00:23:07.910
A simple way to say why is there was never a situation

00:23:07.910 --> 00:23:10.100
of full truth.

00:23:10.100 --> 00:23:11.540
And there never will be.

00:23:11.560 --> 00:23:13.180
So, post-truth doesn't really make sense.

00:23:13.180 --> 00:23:14.320
It's an incoherent concept.

00:23:14.320 --> 00:23:18.900
There is just a lot of propaganda.

00:23:18.900 --> 00:23:23.370
Yeah, and I like Timothy Snyder's framing of this

00:23:23.460 --> 00:23:23.740
.

00:23:23.740 --> 00:23:29.380
And one other thing, which I'm kind of trying to

00:23:29.460 --> 00:23:35.420
get to the foreground again, is most of my work was

00:23:35.420 --> 00:23:39.150
, like the last 10 years, very inspired by Aaron Sw

00:23:39.150 --> 00:23:40.830
artz's comments.

00:23:42.080 --> 00:23:43.930
And I want to bring this also, again, to the

00:23:43.930 --> 00:23:44.620
foreground.

00:23:44.680 --> 00:23:47.380
I think he was really visionary.

00:23:48.420 --> 00:23:54.510
And the most important message in my understanding that he had for

00:23:54.510 --> 00:23:58.260
me was that he told me that this freedom of speech debate

00:23:58.260 --> 00:24:01.460
is actually not helping that much anymore.

00:24:01.460 --> 00:24:06.880
In an environment where ubiquitous networking is the norm.

00:24:06.880 --> 00:24:09.020
So, we have to talk about who gets heard all the

00:24:09.020 --> 00:24:09.430
time.

00:24:09.460 --> 00:24:10.500
It's not about freedoms.

00:24:13.120 --> 00:24:17.580
And, yeah, I think there are lots of reasons to

00:24:17.680 --> 00:24:24.850
be hopeful that the current situation, the current platform situation,

00:24:24.860 --> 00:24:29.480
is about to drastically change in the next few years.

00:24:29.480 --> 00:24:33.330
