00:25:15.780 --> 00:25:17.700
-centrally moderated channels.

00:25:17.700 --> 00:25:20.590
And in the previous years at the conference, when you looked

00:25:20.590 --> 00:25:23.340
at the hashtag traffic, it was always the other way around

00:25:23.420 --> 00:25:23.660
.

00:25:23.660 --> 00:25:24.820
It was always the other way around.

00:25:24.820 --> 00:25:29.290
And I don't know when this flipped.

00:25:29.500 --> 00:25:32.440
It must be something 21, 22, 23, but now

00:25:32.440 --> 00:25:33.480
it has flipped.

00:25:33.480 --> 00:25:39.120
And those people that are in these new alternative systems, they

00:25:39.200 --> 00:25:42.620
